snippet.title: Convolution of Two Sequences in Matlab - Linear Convolution Using Matlab
snippet.description:
Convolution of Two Sequences in Matlab - Linear Convolution Using Matlab

In this tutorial we will write a Linear convolution program in Matlab.

Linear convolution is the basic operation to calculate the output for any linear time invariant system given its input and its impulse response.

For Matlab codes check: 
http://onlineengineers.info/
